metadata.name: Rainbow Feet
metadata.description:
A story of recovery and discovery on a tropical island.

Purchase of this NFT comes with a discount code and a hand signed print of Rainbow Feet.

This NFT is backed by a physical original artwork which is not included in the price and sale of the NFT.
metadata.Discount Code: Use code NFTCOLLECTOR25 at ecmvisionstudio.com to save 25% on purchases including the original painting for this NFT. Contact: info@ecmvisionstudio.com
metadata.Print Gift: Email info@ecmvisionstudio.com to redeem hand signed art print of your NFT. * If you live outside of the USA you'll need to pay for shipping to redeem this offer. Also ECM Vision Studio is not responsible for customs duty fees.
metadata.Original Painting: Original painting is not included. Contact info@ecmvisionstudio.com to see if original is still available for purchase.
